ttp://blog.udn.com/mobile/ASUS/131681487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Fmobile%2FASUS%2F131681487&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=3e7224a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/mobile/ASUS/131681487</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"畫重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">到了 2007 年，中國聯同一眾發展中國家成功推舉香港的陳馮富珍做世衛總幹事，後於 2012 再度連任。她在任內進行重大的選舉改革，執行委員會會閉門推選 3 名候選人到世界衛生大會，然後世界衛生大會再一國一票選出新任的世衛總幹事。新的安排顯然對中國等發展中國家有利，例如非洲國家加起來就有超過 50 票，佔會員數 4 分 1，而在 2017 年，衣索比亞的譚德塞就以 133 票對 50 票，壓倒性擊敗英國的對手。當時，國際專家都對選舉結果表示欣喜，認為可以大大提高世衛的認受性，譚德塞也可以令世衛工作更貼近發展中國家的需要，尤其遏止愛滋病、肺結核和瘧疾在非洲蔓延。</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母地球癌細胞中蟈非洲死左膠"},{"pid":"2333e109a0e5ab0265eeb3af65a2797d96905120","tid":1910624,"uid":4243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"032a92f33eb101106aaa0f608c506f5542220337","tid":1910624,"uid":14653,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"其實我好尊重黑人，係佢令我第一次叫佢做nigga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"Same<br />\n<br />\n但係 nigga 同nigger 係兩個意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc10dab855373d7daa570d5f559fb2d6a6d7266f","tid":1910624,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"大陸想借WHO個公眾知名度等日本可以順利搞奧運<br />\n爆唔爆好似已經冇乜關係<br />\n或者大陸想係奧運入去日本做某D野"},{"pid":"a6069cdac20d7e0763ba34f5178ccc2b2dfe6097","tid":1910624,"uid":15048