認受性，譚德塞也可以令世衛工作更貼近發展中國家的需要，尤其遏止愛滋病、肺結核和瘧疾在非洲蔓延。</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母地球癌細胞中蟈非洲死左膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"非洲咁撚多小國，都戇鳩鳩<br />\n所以大陸咪去收買呢班力架，等佢地可以係聯合國幫支那抬轎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23e004e8952c079d2d1018b88163e6984e0454a","tid":1910624,"uid":260587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"一日8千9百萬個都唔夠啦"},{"pid":"a732cc6fbb0e6756321cd99c132151c9a88c3971","tid":1910624,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cc68dbe382298c89a6d2ce1733d3fc9e8ba6f9c","tid":1910624,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T20:03:37.000Z","msg":"中宣部轄下世衛話，全球每個月需要八千九百萬個口罩<br />\n<br />\n淨係講香港，就當只得四百萬人戴口罩而每人每日只用一個，三十日都一億二千萬個啦<br />\n<br />\n// WHO estimates that each month 89 million medical masks will be required for the COVID-19 response //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/03/who-officials-make-urgent-plea-for-medical-gear-supplies-are-rapidly-depleting.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F03%2F03%2Fwho-officials-make-urgent-plea-for-medical-gear-supplies-are-rapidly-depleting.html&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=26c4a678\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/03/who-officials-make-urgent-plea-for-medical-gear-supplies-are-rapidly-depleting.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:08:23